Okay?

670
00:55:57,726 --> 00:55:59,078
You know
Carmine Falcone.

671
00:55:59,102 --> 00:56:00,579
I told you
it's a mob spot.

672
00:56:00,603 --> 00:56:02,581
You didn't tell me you
had a relationship with him.

673
00:56:02,605 --> 00:56:04,500
I don't have a relationship with him.
 Okay?

