00:56:04,524 --> 00:56:06,485
Pretty.

675
00:56:06,818 --> 00:56:09,696
She a new friend of yours?

676
00:56:13,032 --> 00:56:14,844
I'm not so sure.

677
00:56:14,868 --> 00:56:17,179
Looks like you upset her.

678
00:56:17,203 --> 00:56:19,765
Shall I take this
as a good sign?

